commit.title: [ci] [dune] [opam] Fixes to OPAM and CI target.
commit.message:
[ci] [dune] [opam] Fixes to OPAM and CI target.

The Dune `release` profile is used by OPAM so that should cover the
testing.

We also update the dependencies:

- camlp5: 7.01 had some bugs regarding grammar; we are safer with 7.02
  and that costs nothing,
- lablgtk < 2.18.5 does not support OCaml >= 4.05.0.

commit.message:
[ci] [dune] [opam] Fixes to OPAM and CI target.

The Dune `release` profile is used by OPAM so that should cover the
testing.

We also update the dependencies:

- camlp5: 7.01 had some bugs regarding grammar; we are safer with 7.02
  and that costs nothing,
- lablgtk < 2.18.5 does not support OCaml >= 4.05.0.

user.name: Emilio Jesús Gallego Arias
user.bio: “La perfection est atteinte, non pas lorsqu'il n'y a plus rien à ajouter, mais lorsqu'il n'y a plus rien à retirer.”
